贷款上限，基本能够满足网络小额贷款公司客户需求，一定程度上也可避免非理性的过度借贷，保护消费者合法权益。” 对比来看，此前《网络小额贷款业务管理暂行办法（征求意见稿）》中则规定：对自然人的单户网络小额贷款余额原则上不得超过人民币30万元，不得超过其最近3年年均收入的三分之一，该两项金额中的较低者为贷款金额最高限额。金融监管总局拟发布小贷公司监管规则：网络小贷单户消费贷余额不得超20万 - 21经济网"},"attached_info":"CkAIoYDzuP6dlNBqEAMaCTExMDA5MTY0MCDUxqW2BjAAOJABQBxyCTY2NTE2MzIzNXgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-7e0deca1ea3392f9b8327ed3b506ef90_b.jpg"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"29_1724549473.791121","card_id":"Q_664877011","target":{"id":664877011,"title":"如何评价《黑神话：悟空》第一回「火照黑云」？在难度、剧情、地图和战斗设计方面有哪些值得聊聊？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/664877011","type":"question","created":1724212745,"answer_count":38,"follower_count":91,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[253,1172,601256],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"[图片]"},"attached_info":"Cj8IoYDzuP6dlNBqEAMaCTExMDAyNzkzMyCJzJW2BjAAOFtAHXIJNjY0ODc3MDExeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"热度累计中","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-eaf64b87e6c3db36178f61fdde3374a6_b.jpg"}]}],"description":{"time":"2024-08-25 09:31:14"}}